e":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2760147005","tinyui":"/x/PYCEp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2760147005","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2760147005/Iniciativas+en+Curso","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2760147005"}},{"id":"2975039533","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2975039533","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjk3NTAzOTUzMw==","status":"current","title":"QR en POS","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":1526},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2975039533/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2975039533/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2975039533/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2975039533/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2975039533","tinyui":"/x/LYBTsQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2975039533","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2975039533/QR+en+POS","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2975039533"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"0ecbc81f-c0ca-4895-a0bc-0abc70f888ec\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Este documento representa el tasking y estimaci&oacute;n para Propina QR, a cargo de <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"612e2e8063f7bb006976b761\" ri:local-id=\"16580ef5-66ff-4ca6-9c8c-20b1f8386683\" /></ac:link> </p><p>Las horas estimadas son: 115h ~ 15 d&iacute;as</p><p>Si se inicia ahora:</p><p>Fecha de Inicio: <time datetime=\"2025-10-15\" /> </p><p>Fecha de Entrega: <time datetime=\"2025-11-05\" /> </p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"d127e8c3-3fed-4af2-bc1b-c09b7117def2\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 444.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 176.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 140.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Servicio</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar soporte para parametros:<br />- qr_source = &lsquo;QR-Tip'<br />- server_id: integer <span style=\"color: rgb(255,196,0);\">requerido si qr_source = 'QR-Tip&rsquo;</span><br />- amount_tip:  integer<span style=\"color: rgb(255,196,0);\"> requerido si qr_source = 'QR-Tip&rsquo;</span></p></td><td><p>16h</p></td><td><p>External-commerce-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar soporte para parametros:</p><ul><li><p>qr_source = &lsquo;QR-Tip'</p></li><li><p>server_id: integer <span style=\"color: rgb(255,196,0);\">requerido si qr_source = 'QR-Tip&rsquo;</span></p></li><li><p>amount_tip:  integer<span style=\"color: rgb(255,196,0);\"> requerido si qr_source = 'QR-Tip&rsquo;</span><br /><span style=\"color: rgb(255,196,0);\">Validar en el modelo</span></p></li></ul></td><td><p>16h</p></td><td><p>Selling-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar soporte para par&aacute;metros: </p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Enviar nuevos par&aacute;metros a JPOS (Confirmacion de pago)</p></td><td><p>4h</p></td><td><p>selling-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Enviar nuevos par&aacute;metros a JPOS (Confirmacion de pago)</p></td><td><p>12h</p></td><td><p>external-services</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar nuevos parametros a la request GET <code>payment_hook_by_alias</code> + actualizar stub</p></td><td><p>12h</p></td><td><p>selling-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar nuevos par&aacute;metros a los additional_data en decode_qr_code</p></td><td><p>8h</p></td><td><p>billing-service-public-proxy</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Regla de negocio para no permitir pagos a QR-Tip con tarjeta de cr&eacute;dito, confirm_payment</p></td><td><p>16h</p></td><td><p>billing-service-public-proxy</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Salida a Staging</p><ul><li><p>Integraci&oacute;n de los flujos</p></li><li><p>Creaci&oacute;n y correci&oacute;n de PRs</p></li><li><p>Pruebas locales</p></li><li><p>Armado de ramas</p></li><li><p>Deploy a STG</p></li><li><p>Pruebas iniciales en STG</p></li></ul></td><td><p>16h</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">100</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Gesti&oacute;n 15% (para facturaci&oacute;n, no afecta el desarrollo)</strong></p><p><em>Incluye reuniones de estimaci&oacute;n, planificaci&oacute;n, t&eacute;cnicas y de seguimiento.</em></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">15</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo + Gesti&oacute;n</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>115</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr></tbody></table><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/4244471837"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":1820},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4244471837/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4244471837/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4244471837/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4244471837/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=4244471837","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4244471837/QR+Propina+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/4244471837","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4244471837","tinyui":"/x/HYD9-/","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}